Guendouzi: &quot;I needed to enjoy being on the pitch and to regain confidence. It's what Herta offered me. It's really a choice that I made.&quot;<br />
&quot;In the space of 2 seasons I have played more than 80 games with Arsenal. When you play less, you start to think and it hurts.&quot;<br />
On his journey with France U21: &quot;It was a dream since I was little. Being part of it was wonderful. I still have in the back of my mind to redo a lot of selections, and to be important in the future&quot;
